Package edu.pdx.cs410J.family

Class RemotePersonTest

java.lang.Object
edu.pdx.cs410J.family.RemoteTestCase
edu.pdx.cs410J.family.RemotePersonTest
public class RemotePersonTest
extends RemoteTestCase
This class tests the functionality of implementors of RemotePerson. Note that it just looks up a RemotePerson in the RMI namespace. It doesn't pay any matter what the concrete implementation of RemotePerson is.
